Structure of Rules Grammar

Reserved Words

Rules Grammar has a total of 2 reserved words.

IN LIKE

Special Symbols

Rules Grammar has a total of 12 special symbols.

! && ) || <= >
!= ( , < == >=

Comment

Comment Block

A Comment Block group is starts with a /* and ends when a */ is read. It has the following format:

/* ... */

When the system is reading a Comment Block, text will be analyzed as a series of characters. So, anytime a */ is read, the group will end. This includes cases where the */ is embedded in other lexical structures such as string literals.

No other groups can be nested within this one.

Comment Line

A Comment Line group is starts with a // and ends when a NewLine is read. It has the following format:

// ... NewLine

When the system is reading a Comment Line, text will be analyzed as a series of characters. So, anytime a NewLine is read, the group will end. This includes cases where the NewLine is embedded in other lexical structures such as string literals. The NewLine is not considered part of the group.

No other groups can be nested within this one.

Syntax

Boolean-Expression :
  Conditional-AND-Expression

Conditional-AND-Expression :
  Conditional-AND-Expression && Conditional-OR-Expression
  Conditional-OR-Expression

Conditional-OR-Expression :
  Conditional-OR-Expression || Equality-Expression
  Equality-Expression

Equality-Expression :
  Value-Constant-Expression == Variable-Expression
  Value-Constant-Expression != Variable-Expression
  Variable-Expression == Value-Constant-Expression
  Variable-Expression != Value-Constant-Expression
  In-Expression

Group-Expression :
  ( Boolean-Expression )

In-Expression :
  Variable-Expression IN ( Date-Tuple-Expression )
  Variable-Expression IN ( Numeric-Tuple-Expression )
  Variable-Expression IN ( String-Tuple-Expression )
  Like-Expression

Date-Tuple-Expression :
  Date-Constant-Expression , Date-Tuple-Expression
  Date-Constant-Expression

Numeric-Tuple-Expression :
  Numeric-Constant-Expression , Numeric-Tuple-Expression
  Numeric-Constant-Expression

String-Tuple-Expression :
  String-Constant-Expression , String-Tuple-Expression
  String-Constant-Expression

Like-Expression :
  Variable-Expression LIKE String-Constant-Expression
  Relational-Expression

Relational-Expression :
  Value-Constant-Expression < Variable-Expression
  Value-Constant-Expression > Variable-Expression
  Value-Constant-Expression <= Variable-Expression
  Value-Constant-Expression >= Variable-Expression
  Variable-Expression < Value-Constant-Expression
  Variable-Expression > Value-Constant-Expression
  Variable-Expression <= Value-Constant-Expression
  Variable-Expression >= Value-Constant-Expression
  Reference-Expression

Reference-Expression :
  Reference
  Unary-Expression

Unary-Expression :
  ! Group-Expression
  Group-Expression

Date-Constant-Expression :
  Date

Numeric-Constant-Expression :
  Integer
  Real

String-Constant-Expression :
  String

Value-Constant-Expression :
  Date-Constant-Expression
  Numeric-Constant-Expression
  String-Constant-Expression

Variable-Expression :
  Variable

"Name"                                  = 'Rules Grammar'
"Version"                               = '4.0.0.0'
"Author"                                = 'Eric.Berens@bestbuy.com (NA\a028719)'
"About"                                 = 'Copyright Best Buy Co., Inc.'
"Case Sensitive"                        = 'False' !DEFAULT
"Character Mapping"                     = 'Windows-1252' !DEFAULT
"Auto Whitespace"                       = 'True' !DEFAULT
!"Virtual Terminals"                    = ''
"Start Symbol"                          = <Boolean Expression>
 
! ======================================================================================================================================================================================================
! Character Sets
! ======================================================================================================================================================================================================
 
{Reference Character Set}               = {Alphanumeric}    + [-./:\_|]     ! -./0123456789:ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ\_abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz|
{String Character Set}                  = {Printable}       - ["]           ! {Space}!#$%&'()*+,-./0123456789:;<=>?@ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ[\]^_`abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz{|}~{NBSP}
{Variable Character Set}                = {Alphanumeric}    + [-./:\_|]     ! -./0123456789:ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ\_abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz|
 
! ======================================================================================================================================================================================================
! Comments
! ======================================================================================================================================================================================================
 
Comment Start                           = '/*'
Comment End                             = '*/'
Comment Line                            = '//'
 
! ======================================================================================================================================================================================================
! Rules
! ======================================================================================================================================================================================================
 
! Additive Rule
!<Additive Expression>                   ::= <Additive Expression>           '+'     <Multiplicative Expression>
!                                         |  <Additive Expression>           '-'     <Multiplicative Expression>
 
!                                         |  <Multiplicative Expression>
 
! Boolean Expression Rule
<Boolean Expression>                    ::= <Conditional AND Expression>
 
! Conditional AND Rule
<Conditional AND Expression>            ::= <Conditional AND Expression>    '&&'    <Conditional OR Expression>
 
                                         |  <Conditional OR Expression>
 
! Conditional OR Rule
<Conditional OR Expression>             ::= <Conditional OR Expression>     '||'    <Equality Expression>
 
                                         |  <Equality Expression>
 
! Equality Rule
<Equality Expression>                   ::= <Value Constant Expression>     '=='    <Variable Expression>
                                         |  <Value Constant Expression>     '!='    <Variable Expression>
 
                                         |  <Variable Expression>           '=='    <Value Constant Expression>
                                         |  <Variable Expression>           '!='    <Value Constant Expression>
 
                                         |  <In Expression>
 
! Group Rule
<Group Expression>                      ::= '(' <Boolean Expression> ')'
 
! In Rule
!   @Variable IN (####-##-##[, <Date Tuple Expression>])
!   @Variable IN (#[, <Numeric Tuple Expression>])
!   @Variable IN (#.#[, <Numeric Tuple Expression>])
!   @Variable IN (\"...\"[, <String Tuple Expression>])
<In Expression>                         ::= <Variable Expression>           'IN'    '('    <Date Tuple Expression>       ')'
                                         |  <Variable Expression>           'IN'    '('    <Numeric Tuple Expression>    ')'
                                         |  <Variable Expression>           'IN'    '('    <String Tuple Expression>     ')'
 
                                         |  <Like Expression>
 
! Date Tuple Rule
<Date Tuple Expression>                 ::= <Date Constant Expression>      ','     <Date Tuple Expression>
                                         |  <Date Constant Expression>
 
! Numeric Tuple Rule
<Numeric Tuple Expression>              ::= <Numeric Constant Expression>   ','     <Numeric Tuple Expression>
                                         |  <Numeric Constant Expression>
 
! String Tuple Rule
<String Tuple Expression>               ::= <String Constant Expression>    ','     <String Tuple Expression>
                                         |  <String Constant Expression>
 
! Like Rule
!   @Variable LIKE "%..."
!   @Variable LIKE "...%"
!   @Variable LIKE "%...%"
<Like Expression>                       ::= <Variable Expression>           'LIKE'  <String Constant Expression>
 
                                         |  <Relational Expression>
 
! Multiplicative Rule
!<Multiplicative Expression>             ::= <Multiplicative Expression>     '*'     <Negate Expression>
!                                         |  <Multiplicative Expression>     '/'     <Negate Expression>
!                                         |  <Multiplicative Expression>     '%'     <Negate Expression>
 
!                                         |  <Negate Expression>
 
! Negate Rule
!<Negate Expression>                     ::= '-' <Numeric Constant Expression>
 
!                                         |  '-' <Variable Expression>
 
!                                         |  <Numeric Constant Expression>
 
!                                         |  <Variable Expression>
 
! Relational
<Relational Expression>                 ::= <Value Constant Expression>     '<'     <Variable Expression>
                                         |  <Value Constant Expression>     '>'     <Variable Expression>
                                         |  <Value Constant Expression>     '<='    <Variable Expression>
                                         |  <Value Constant Expression>     '>='    <Variable Expression>
 
                                         |  <Variable Expression>           '<'     <Value Constant Expression>
                                         |  <Variable Expression>           '>'     <Value Constant Expression>
                                         |  <Variable Expression>           '<='    <Value Constant Expression>
                                         |  <Variable Expression>           '>='    <Value Constant Expression>
 
                                         |  <Reference Expression>
 
! Reference Rule
!   {{Reference}}
<Reference Expression>                  ::= Reference
 
                                         |  <Unary Expression>
 
! Unary Rule
<Unary Expression>                      ::= '!' <Group Expression>
 
                                         |  <Group Expression>
 
! Date Constant Rule
<Date Constant Expression>              ::= Date
 
! Numeric Constant Rule
<Numeric Constant Expression>           ::= Integer
                                         |  Real
 
! String Constant Rule
<String Constant Expression>            ::= String
 
! Value Constant Rule
<Value Constant Expression>             ::= <Date Constant Expression>
                                         |  <Numeric Constant Expression>
                                         |  <String Constant Expression>
 
! Variable Rule
<Variable Expression>                   ::= Variable
 
! ======================================================================================================================================================================================================
! Terminals
! ======================================================================================================================================================================================================

Integer                                 = {Number}+                                                                         ! #
Real                                    = {Number}+'.'{Number}+                                                             ! #.#

String                                  = '"'({String Character Set}|'\'{Printable})*'"'                                    ! ("String"|"\"Quoted String\"")
